name: Skyrol® SH82 (200ga) Polyester
description: Skyrol® SH82 (200ga) Polyester is an optically clear, glossy, two side chemically treated film. It provides an enhanced adhesion to various inks and adhesives. SH82 film is available in a range of thickness from 200ga to 750ga, and is used for high quality printing and solvent coating applications. SH82 film is FDA approved for direct food contact in compliance with FDA 21 CFR 177.1630 (f).
